# Flo8 Frontend Specification

## Project Overview
Flo8 is a frontend application that provides a workspace environment for creating and managing flow-based interfaces.




## Core Architecture

src/
  ├── components/      # Reusable UI components
  │   ├── ui/         # Shadcn components
  │   └── workspace/  # Flow workspace components
  │   └── dashboard/  # dashboard components
  │   └── user/  		 # User components
  ├── stores/         # State management
  ├── styles/         # Global styles and Tailwind config
  ├── types/          # TypeScript type definitions
  ├── pages/          # Pages
  ├── utils/          # Utility functions
  ├── config/          # App config, where features can be enabled or disabled
  ├── hooks/          # custom Hooks
  └── services/       # API and service layer



